Package: tweetio
Title: Really, Really, Ridiculously Fast Tweet Data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Brendan", "Knapp", 
           email = "brendan.g.knapp@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3284-4972"))
Description: 
    `{tweetio}`'s primary goal is to read raw tweets into data frames as fast as possible,
    whether the data came directly from the Twitter API, a database dump, or from
    `{rtweet}` or another package. It also provides routines to transform tweet data into 
    useful structures and write the data to useful file formats.
